{"tid":1654621,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本冬天一問","createTime":"2019-10-14T16:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T23:36:17.000Z","uid":258782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff990e671571d53aca12928d3aaef24571e9f58","tid":1654621,"uid":258782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟想冬天去日本睇下雪，暫定1月<br />\n想問下使唔使帶雪地眼鏡個D？（雖然我唔滑雪）"},{"pid":"cb519813a8b7cdae38b485c436902f40239284f3","tid":1654621,"uid":140335,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"唔洗<br />\n我年年都係背心短褲加對香港製紅黑人字拖過去<br />\n唔洗帶呢啲野<br />\n<br />\n利申：怕凍"},{"pid":"fd1cd0e92fa0aee659719641fa85457e1e89efb4","tid":1654621,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"緊急，聽日vtc Di院校開始停課，為期三日，到18日，將會係CCTV片段剛一個月，唔好俾佢del片，漏夜宣傳<br />\n<br />\n（VTC同學速入)讓陳同學沉冤得雪！！！還其家人一個公道！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654230</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話，幫手推同share岀去，等聽日多啲人集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跪求幫手推呢個先，聽日要人，但我地唔想提早俾校方知而令佢地關校，所以咁夜先岀稿，求share至fb,ws,tg各群組<br />\n另外，部分ive設施對公眾開放的"},{"pid":"fad1104376a906ebc137a519360fd72afbb3ec7b","tid":1654621,"uid":96032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔滑雪就帶定副黑超就算啦<br />\n未必用得著，睇天氣同地點<br />\n有雲冇雲，市區定效區，已經好大分別<br />\n不過帶定冇壞"},{"pid":"101677a90d50a99d2396cbeafd69fb2291c6a9fa","tid":1654621,"uid":96032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔滑雪就帶定副黑超就算啦<br />\n未必用得著，睇天氣同地點<br />\n有雲冇雲，市區定<span style=\"color: red;\">郊</span>區，已經好大分別<br />\n不過帶定冇壞</blockquote>"},{"pid":"72d56259e21118631e5807b63d4fb79cb891e86c","tid":1654621,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,